data.description: Welcome to this fabulous opportunity located in a well desired neighborhood in the City of Pittsburgh. Come see this beautiful Ranchette Style Home with excellent curb appeal and bring your ideas along with your creative design to bring this beauty back to life as this home needs a little TLC. This spacious 1839 sq/ft home is situated on an 8295 sq/ft lot. This home features 3 bedrooms, 2 full baths, a formal living room and family room with a cozy gas fireplace, and a two car garage with extra space for possible RV parking. This home is perfect for family fun with a California sun room with bar, an in ground swimming pool, and outdoor fire pit. Home also comes with Solar System and second driveway on side of house for guest parking. Home is close Shopping, schools, and parks. Easy access to freeways. Hurry, home is priced to sell and won't be on the market for long.
